Ogg/Vorbis/Header version 0.01
============================

A Perl wrapper for the libao audio library, a modular cross-platfrom
PCM output library.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Inline::C, libao

Inline::C is available from CPAN.  Libao is available from xiph.org

